          <text>WCB activity</text>
        </annotation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">10</infon>
        <offset>1581</offset>
        <text>WCB activity was less consistent and primarily constrained to colder, high nutrient and low chlorophyll waters.
</text>
